Features


Generative AI Models: Leverages advanced neural networks for improved translation accuracy and fluency.
User Personalization: Allows users to customize translations based on specific datasets and preferences.
Real-time Translation: Provides instant feedback and adjustments during the translation process.
Multi-language Support: Supports a wide range of languages for diverse user needs.
Third-party Integration: Easily integrates with popular platforms and utilities for extended functionality.

Technologies Used
Programming Languages: Python
Frameworks: TensorFlow, Flask, React
APIs: Google Translate API

